item.title: About
item.description: Hi, I’m Ed Goodwin. I live in Houston, TX with my wife and three kids. I play guitar (badly) and listen to music way too loud for everyone’s tastes. I’m also a huge soccer fan, and am a die-hard supporter of the Houston Dynamo and Tottenham Hotspurs. I’m also one of the founders of Rana Analytics, a boutique consulting company focused on helping customers leverage the OneStream platform to accelerate their financial analytics.
